ocuments, from the Einstein-Szilard letter to President Roosevelt (1939) to the announcement of the Strategic Defense Initiative by President Reagan (1983), have been added as appendixes.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 31. Jan 2022) 4aPolitics -- United States. 4aSecurity Studies -- National Security. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / General.2bisacsh1 aHerken, Gregg, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLeone, Richard C., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978080476439140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780804764391423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780804764391/original  aGBV-deGruyter-alles